[SN]TITLE[SN]
Man dies following Aberdeen flat fire

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man has died in hospital following a flat fire in Aberdeen on Christmas Eve.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Emergency services were called to the incident in the Nellfield Place area at about 20:00.
Firefighters found the man in the property.
Police said he was taken to Aberdeen Royal Infirmary but later died. A force spokesman said inquiries into the cause of the fire were ongoing.
